      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/us-financial-regulators-restart-work-long-delayed-compensation-rules-2024-05-06/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国三名金融监管机构已恢复了一项拖延已久的规则制定项目，以使金融公司的高管薪酬计划对风险更加敏感。]]></description>
